      <title>Docker 安装青龙面板+机器人控制</title>
      <link href="/2021/11/12/docker/"/>
      <url>/2021/11/12/docker/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>青龙面板与大家熟知的宝塔面板类似，可以通过此面板安装各类脚本实现自己的各种想法。最近这款面板十分火热，在这里给大家分享一种功能，通过docker搭载实现安装青龙面板，并且实现自动化设置，这里就不废话了，直接上教程！</p><blockquote><p>作者：夙渊君</p></blockquote><h4 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h4><ul><li>VPS一台 </li><li>SSH终端工具</li></ul><h3 id="在VPS上安装Docker"><a href="#在VPS上安装Docker" class="headerlink" title="在VPS上安装Docker"></a>在VPS上安装Docker</h3><p>在这里我选择阿里云 Ubuntu系统上面安装Docker,当然任何Docker平台都是可以的，比如群晖、威联通、Unraid…</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#使用官方安装脚本自动安装</span><br><span class="line">curl -fsSL https:<span class="comment">//get.docker.com | bash -s docker --mirror Aliyun</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">安装完Docker后，正式开始安装青龙面板</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">``</span><span class="string">`javascript</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">docker pull whyour/qinglong</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>docker run -dit <br>   -v $PWD/ql/config:/ql/config <br>   -v $PWD/ql/log:/ql/log <br>   -v $PWD/ql/db:/ql/db <br>   -p 5700:5700 <br>   –name qinglong <br>   –hostname qinglong <br>   –restart always <br>   whyour/qinglong:latest</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">初次访问 http://&lt;自己ip&gt;:5700,使用 admin/adminadmin 登陆，提示已初始化密码</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">去自己映射目录config下找 auth.json，查看里面的 password</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>docker exec -it qinglong cat /ql/config/auth.json</p><p>拉取脚本</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker exec -it qinglong ql repo https://github.com/curtinlv/JD-Script.git </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker exec -it qinglong ql repo https://github.com/he1pu/JDHelp.git "jd_|jx_|getJDCookie" "activity|backUp|Coupon" "^jd[^_]|USER"</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker exec -it qinglong ql repo https://github.com/panghu999/jd_scripts.git "jd_|jx_|getJDCookie" "activity|backUp|Coupon|jd_try|format_" "^jd[^_]|USER"</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="安装花语面板"><a href="#安装花语面板" class="headerlink" title="安装花语面板"></a>安装花语面板</h3><p>我们需要一个获取cookie的工具，这里使用花语和青龙来配合使用</p><ul><li>下载好相应的JDC文件</li><li>把JDC上传到青龙目录 /ql下</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo -i（获取root权限）</span><br><span class="line">cd /root/ql（进入青龙文件夹路径）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>chmod 777 JDC<br>./JDC</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>vi config.toml</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nohup ./JDC</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">### 安装机器人</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* 在botfather申请token  2009987606:AAF4AHMF7s6J3SBLwB8PX-ScOPvep3mcqD0</span><br><span class="line">* 获取userid                    1787435656</span><br><span class="line">* Api  id        </span><br><span class="line">* hash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">在config文件中把toStartBot=""改为"ture"</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>docker exec -it qinglong ql bot</p>]]></content>
      
      
